hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[搵工要小心，切勿中美容教育傳銷陷阱]  大學生小心職場陷阱</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164225%2Fpage%2F1&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3591b9cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=36842fb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"條友假膠來，點會pin你"},{"pid":"68daf7e55c5878c63ce26b331d5f936dd76f579b","tid":2008803,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111f4e9a6256dc63a315d879ce6742c0ae475210","tid":2008803,"uid":316700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31a2bd245a768f883f9a3d4d297832bcc90ab1de","tid":2008803,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9915ccd44d4dff4964cc755347a707495dda921d","tid":2008803,"uid":316700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"過來人想指點一下班fg,，今時今日咁嘅時勢搵工真係唔好咁揀擇，真係搵唔到可以做住義工先，寫落cv有著數。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2006187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2006187</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n傻西人格分裂樓豬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"要我講幾多次？<br />\n依個acc 成team一齊run<br />\n早午晚替四更咁多人上手開咩post有幾出期<br />\n唔通我唔知有起㡳功能咩叻唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"run?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你開公司？分四更上線賺錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"想要佢條team啲個人資料同黑幕可以留tg."},{"pid":"b1d9ac5b35fcb0f65cfd7b1fe5697f01234234de","tid":2008803,"uid":338136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64822c3b5e0917380283eeaf1e8d42615ea89f39","tid":2008803,"uid":200686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"07dc36953e87f1b64c4a7e27beebd83cc22cf390","tid":2008803,"uid":338136,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"咩係hkue?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-