e":"2020-05-10T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"真係未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"我寧願讀vtc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼知係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"翻足堂，就可以穩穩咁畢業啦"},{"pid":"802679954447ae765c0ce9df601023439f047aae","tid":2008803,"uid":357199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd6161a75f9a14dfae104cb7dfc59bd20f547959","tid":2008803,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"如題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:34:44.000Z","msg":"唔好on 9 <br />\n香港咁多學校唔要要呢間？"},{"pid":"331461178d98a03706f6fdd1cfa60ef084fc2acc","tid":2008803,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b646824cfcfacf48e5a96cfe4121215e10328d74","tid":2008803,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:10:12.000Z","msg":"間野改咗名做uche 喇（樓主pin this)<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span style=\"color: green;\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=ccd42509\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3fd6e38a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[搵工要小心，切勿中美容教育傳銷陷阱]  大學生小心職場陷阱</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164225%2Fpage%2F1&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3591b9cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=36842fb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"騙徒Crystal Li李婉瑩新電話號碼: 91570141<br />\n<br />\n呢個騙徒係大陸人，由汕尾移民落黎香港，專呃d DSE 學生去報冇資歷級別 (HKQF) 嘅課程，另外會呃女性去美容院 <br />\n<br />\n更多資訊： <br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3D62kedb7g&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=c33067b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3Di4waqbjt&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=f0ace3c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt</a> <br />\n<br />\n除咗美容，仲有SELL 教育，中醫，脫毛，投資等等<br />\n<br />\nChampion Team 另一成員 <br />\n如果去見工會見到佢 <br />\n(與Sam Chau Wing Sum 周詠森，Hugo Wong 及 三金合作） <br />\n<br />\n行業：教育及美容傳銷 <br />\n花名：Crystal Li / 水晶梨 <br />\n中文全名：李婉瑩 <br />\n英文全名：Li Wan Ying <br />\n常用工作電話：91570141（Updated) <br />\n另一工作電話：51610763 (可以 iMessage) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f44ohbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff44ohbs.jpg&h=a018e3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VbXiY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VbXiY9.jpg&h=a59da781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ModKJqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModKJqQ.jpg&h=a38f4662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騙徒Crystal Li 與 英皇金融集團營業代表之合照<br />\n<br />\n警告： 投資有風險，參加任何投資課程及買任何投資產品前，請先了解清楚有關風險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RLiRgw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RLiRgw.jpg&h=52fa49bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzJHyuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzJHyuS.png&h=fa34c437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AJgCWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AJgCWx.jpg&h=8f958111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AzWCWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AzWCWy.jpg&h=3044c77a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d0726be08eb4ced27d1d27196334100962fa42b","tid":2008803,"uid":257875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T13:06:19.000Z","msg":"知咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今時今日都有人問呢個問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZXBWRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZXBWRE.png&h=69636a59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"632da19c5eaa88cbe25a07995c372c76e96677c5","tid":2008803,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d0726be08eb4ced27d1d27196334100962fa42b","tid":2008803,"uid":257875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T13:06:19.000Z","msg":"知咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今時今日都有人問呢個問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZXBWRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZXBWRE.png&h=69636a59&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"間野好似改咗名"}]}